response.original_title: Komik Organik: The Comedy of Rex Navarrete
response.overview: REX NAVARRETE comes back with this third live recording from the historic San Jose Improv. After 20 years of stand-up comedy, he continues to pull out all the stops on Filipino-American phenomena, from Imperialist Foodie Nations to world-boxing champion Manny Pacquiao. If you are a Pinoy of just know a few Pinoys as a F.O.P. (Friend of Pinoys), then this is your next level into the insights of clearly one the funniest ethnic groups to ever decide to come to America. After the release of his three live CD's and live DVD's, "Hella Pinoy" and "Badass Madapaka", this recording will truly become a multi-cult classic.
response.title: Komik Organik: The Comedy of Rex Navarrete
